Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:09.62,Signs,,0,0,0,,Damn, I'm late...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.14,0:00:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are Genta and Mitsuhiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.11,0:00:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, look at them...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.24,0:00:39.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the... that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.04,0:00:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.46,0:00:41.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hand slipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.71,0:00:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because you twirled it with too much force!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.88,0:00:46.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only two days remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:48.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm all worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the lengthy flower clock renovation had been finished...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:56.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A ceremony to commemorate the occasion was in order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.26,0:01:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They needed some elementary schoolgirl\Nbaton twirlers for the event...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.81,0:01:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} was selected.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why she's been practicing every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.53,0:01:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that person!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like fog clearing up in a swoosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:23.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see through both romance and cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A baffling case occurred in the park.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only the flower clock saw the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.55,0:01:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:33.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that guy is the stalker?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.41,0:03:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was here yesterday and the day before too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.41,0:03:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good thing we came here as bodyguards!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.13,0:03:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi's scared of you, y'know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know who we're dealing with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He reeks of booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.36,0:04:01.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he climbs that high while in a drunken state...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is he drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:06.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he had extremely foul alcohol breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he should fall from that height, he\Nwon't walk away with a light injury!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For making you wake up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.02,0:04:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone already volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, we can't possibly let you go alone to a place where\Nsuch a disgusting guy is hanging around, Yoshida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.49,0:04:45.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:49.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I swear I've seen them somewhere else...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hat and coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.91,0:04:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he someone you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.46,0:04:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't be sure of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet I'd recognize him if I see his face, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:59.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You couldn't see his face when he breathed on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:03.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was deeply concealed by his hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.13,0:05:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Next Day
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.97,0:05:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he going to come today too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he does, I'm totally gonna reveal his true identity!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's our guy, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is he dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:27.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.28,0:05:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wound on his cheek...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did the tip of that hand cut him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.54,0:05:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he was a pretty thin man...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.72,0:05:44.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy was a stalker!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.89,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was targeting Ayumi, who was practicing early in the morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came yesterday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.85,0:05:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He looked really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:05:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he climbed up this arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.27,0:06:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was drunk and climbed the arch?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.78,0:06:04.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very close to falling down, I should add.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.40,0:06:07.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His body indeed reeked of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.75,0:06:09.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the security guard who patrolled the park last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.25,0:06:15.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.71,0:06:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what time did you patrol around this flower clock?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I started my patrol shift at 3:00 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:27.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I checked around the flower clock at approximately 3:50.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was the body there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:30.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't find any trace of the flowers being disturbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.52,0:06:37.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has got to be an accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:39.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.10,0:06:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you came!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan was late coming home, so Ran told me to come get him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The position of the stone number 6 on\Nthe clock is right beneath the arch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.74,0:06:53.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, he climbed up the arch and fell while inebriated...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And hit his head on this stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.71,0:07:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the man's time of death was between 3:50 and 4:30 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:09.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason being he suffered from a slash\Nwound by the clock's long hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.55,0:07:15.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the clock was pointing at the thirty -minute\Nposition after he fell to his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What time did you guys arrive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.98,0:07:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was about 5:20.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:27.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That goes to show the man's cheek was slashed at 4:30.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.11,0:07:31.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you take these children back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.49,0:07:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.87,0:07:39.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you here to pick them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:43.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The death was an accident, and all that's\Nleft is to confirm the man's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have a good idea about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.63,0:07:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was a painter, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since that person had traces of paint on his hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.64,0:07:57.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Couldn't he merely have gotten paint on him somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:02.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he even had old, dried paint in the creases of his palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.48,0:08:04.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he worked with paint a lot when he was alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.36,0:08:07.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:09.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weill, that's the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.74,0:08:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no need for Sleeping Kogorou\Nto make an appearance time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:14.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.95,0:08:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right you guys, let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.16,0:08:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.84,0:08:22.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About where I met that man before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:30.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He came to my place once before to buy alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.88,0:08:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to the testimony from Genta's father...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:36.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found out that the man had worked\Nat a nearby signboard factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's Yoda Shousaku, a member of our staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.22,0:08:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he died after getting hammered?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:45.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds just like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.19,0:08:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean he was a bad drunk by nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He becomes arrogant when he's drunk and really stirs things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.70,0:08:54.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.53,0:08:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that one is Yoda's last work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:08:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.01,0:09:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This part is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last month, Yoda tried to mount that\Nsign while under the influence...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.83,0:09:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he fell down with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy Yoda has been afraid of heights ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Taking days off from work and binging on booze.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had acrophobia?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you give me more information in detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real culprit had us in their trap all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:32.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was afraid of heights.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could that kind of guy possibly climb up an arch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, who was that man that we saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was likely the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not knowing that Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had acrophobia...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:51.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They pretended to be Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and repeatedly acted strangely...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In order to make the murder look like an accidental death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:56.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They must've used the time during Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make you into a witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:07.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think they used Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} for something\Nlike that—it's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.48,0:10:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:11.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're definitely going to find the culprit ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.73,0:10:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Revisit a hundred times"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Basic investigation dogma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, dawg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:28.83,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi Kyouichirou (30)\NPhysical Education Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.20,0:10:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Kawaguchi Kyouichirou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A P.E. instructor at a high school in Niigata?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:31.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.18,0:10:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,DO you know Yoda Shousaku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I know him very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.59,0:10:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hatred for him knows no bounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three years ago, while Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was still\Nteaching art at the same high school...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.43,0:10:51.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had an illicit infatuation towards your girlfriend,\Nwho was an English teacher at that same school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One day, when Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} took her for a ride against her will...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.78,0:10:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got into an accident, and your girlfriend was the one who died.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.16,0:11:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was not an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:06.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoda disguised it as an accident while\Nin fact murdering my girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.45,0:11:12.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And since a week ago, you've been staying at a\Nbusiness hotel in front of Haido Station, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors that Yoda lived around\Nhere, so I came to find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, can you tell us your whereabouts\Nbetween 3:50 and 4:30 this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:25.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it about my alibi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm in luck then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can confirm it with 119...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About when I called an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An ambulance?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.53,0:11:38.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was being careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.65,0:11:42.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I accidentally ingested a button\Nbattery when taking medicine tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.41,0:11:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I called an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, turned out to be a normal button when\Nthe doctors checked on me, so I was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty sure it was about 3:30 when they\Ntransported me to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it was after 4:30 when they discharged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From that hospital to this park...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll take a good twenty minutes no matter how you rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.47,0:12:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask the hospital too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.60,0:12:09.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do that, you'll definitely understand\Nthat I couldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.23,0:12:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please investigate carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person just now has an alibi of being in\Nthe hospital between 3:30 and 4:30, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.24,0:12:24.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The method of drugging the victim to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Injuring his cheek with the clock hand in advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally killing him by hitting his head against the clock's number\Nstone after leaving the hospital sounds possible, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.32,0:12:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it may be possible given the time frame since his death\Nwas estimated to be between 4:00 and past 5:00 AM...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fact that they assured us the victim's cheek wound\Nwas inflicted post-mortem nullifies your theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.97,0:12:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.18,0:12:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus, they said that traces of stone shards from\Nthe clock were found in the laceration...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.89,0:12:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt the scene of crime was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:12:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle said so after he heard it from the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you used Detective Mouri's voice again\Nto make the police officers talk, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about the paint on the victim's hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything characteristic about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, they said it was normal paint\Nthat can be found anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he was a signboard maker...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no surprise that he had paint on his hand, now is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they said he had been taking days off work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.97,0:13:31.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the fact that there were new paint marks raises a flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.35,0:13:35.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this door for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:37.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Must be the clock's machine room.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The chain lock securing the door was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does that tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey,hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:49.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you kids doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.62,0:13:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone broke the chain lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.46,0:13:56.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who could've done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:13:59.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This door leads to the clock's machine room, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But during the flower clock's repair, we've installed\Nwhat we call "moveless drive units"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.97,0:14:08.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a new type of drive system inserted directly in the hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So we emptied the clockwork in the\Nroom and converted it into storage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's paint spilled on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.69,0:14:19.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same color as the paint on the victim's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:24.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's dry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he didn't get the paint from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:29.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, how does it look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owww...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.29,0:14:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Young boy, let's go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan Episode 631\NFansub Release by DCTP\NRipped by DJ VK & Innushka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:55.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you figure out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.52,0:15:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's no doubt that Kawaguchi guy is our man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he has an alibi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number stones are firmly affixed to the ground\Nso the crime scene was no doubt at the flower clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the only time to cut his cheek with the long hand\Nwithout disturbing the flowers on the clock...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Had to be half past the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:18.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:23.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At 4:30, the only possible candidate, he just got out of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.83,0:15:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's play on the seesaw now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.91,0:15:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:31.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:34.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hit my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:37.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you skinned your cheek!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.31,0:15:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:40.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can be done this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.15,0:15:45.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever, let's follow him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.70,0:15:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find out something?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.00,0:16:05.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:07.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:09.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, you showed up at a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.55,0:16:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry on home and do your homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this you have to tell us about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:24.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of my drinking pals is friends with Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he let me in on a surprising fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprising fact?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.57,0:16:34.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, ever since Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} fell from\Nmounting a signboard last month...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's developed a serious case of acrophobia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already knew that ages ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:41.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.29,0:16:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the fact that he caused a traffic accident in his hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And let a woman die in the process?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've obtained information on that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.02,0:16:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That woman was actually my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:55.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:57.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Kawaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Currently your prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:01.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.77,0:17:04.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the gang's all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.85,0:17:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, why have you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before I return to Niigata, I figure I should\Npay Yoda's scene of death a last visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.74,0:17:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, we can't let you go yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.70,0:17:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, didn't you already confirm with the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you know that I'm not the culprit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.75,0:17:26.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shall be excused, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.63,0:17:27.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:31.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Round 'n round I go...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.88,0:17:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twirl twirl!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.26,0:17:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My line of questioning isn't quite finished yet, Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you're that famous Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.56,0:17:48.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What more is there you need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.36,0:17:53.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regarding Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s alibi, can you recount it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.57,0:17:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was at the hospital the entire time\Nduring 3:30 and 4:30 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it takes twenty minutes from that hospital to here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.12,0:18:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Simply put, I couldn't possibly commit the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.50,0:18:08.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you could've come here at 5:00, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.75,0:18:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I did come at 5:00, there'd be nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:16.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You confined Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} inside the flower\Nclock's machine room beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.97,0:18:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And arrived here at 5:00 to finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.47,0:18:23.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Balderdash.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:26.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, the cheek wound on the body can't be explained.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It so happens to be 5:00 now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Twelve hours ago, Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} by smashing\Nhis head against the number 6 stone on the flower clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.11,0:18:41.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after cutting his cheek with the long\Nhand which was pointing at 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.58,0:18:45.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put down his body near the number 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.70,0:18:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without disturbing the flowers, how the heck\Ndid I manage to walk near the number 12?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.08,0:18:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From where the number 5 is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:55.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could've stepped across the hedge and onto\Nthe stone without deranging the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.34,0:18:59.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And while carrying Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s body in your arms...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.18,0:19:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You walked atop the hands of the flower clock towards\Nthe tip of the long hand with it pointing at 12...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.27,0:19:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wounded Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cheek with the tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.31,0:19:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you retraced your steps by walking on the hands again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:13.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.53,0:19:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use acting so tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the flower clock saw was the entirety of your crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it silently told me the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.45,0:19:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are minute traces of blood on the stone near the number 12.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stone and the clock hands weren't making contact to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since you were stepping on it while carrying Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:41.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand warped down and touched the stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:46.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the blood coming from Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cheek\Nwhen you cut him traveled down the hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And got on that stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:52.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should be able to match it with Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood after lab tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if that's the case, you still can't pin it on me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.57,0:20:00.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we investigate the surface of the hands, we should\Nbe able to find traces that match your shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.63,0:20:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ignoring the short hand, for the long hand\Nto stay supported by that stone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.53,0:20:09.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that you.can step on top of it without crushing\Nthe flowers, you only have one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be impossible for you to walk back\Nand forth and cut Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s cheek...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:17.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And wipe away your shoe prints in such a short time frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:19.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You may not be aware of this, but Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nleft a message indicating you're the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.93,0:20:30.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.27,0:20:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Show the inspector the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.81,0:20:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you too, Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:48.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s message is in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to find it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:55.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.88,0:21:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was spilled on the floor was in fact fluorescent paint.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it's become dark in here, the light started to show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.31,0:21:11.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle Kogorou said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.48,0:21:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fluorescent paint will not glow in the dark\Nunless it was exposed to light beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since it was dark in here the entire time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.48,0:21:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It didn't glow during the time Kawaguchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nlocked Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} in; that's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:27.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He chose to enter and exit this place during\Nthe night to avoid surveillance...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.74,0:21:30.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why it wasn't exposed to light even with the door open.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But where exactly is the message?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:41.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kawaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.71,0:21:45.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who was being held hostage here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.71,0:21:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noticed the spilled paint and left his final message with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:55.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately for him, it was the same color\Nas the spilled fluorescent paint on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.31,0:22:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s message couldn't\Nbe seen under bright daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:05.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We shall investigate this room thoroughly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We will definitely pick up evidence of Yoda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s confinement\Nand traces of your breaking and entering!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.12,0:22:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought it was a perfect plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.68,0:22:16.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.92,0:22:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One week later than originally planned...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:53.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opening ceremony for the flower clock finally took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.26,0:24:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I shall put an end to your allotted time by way of a formless sword."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"From: The Guardian of Time."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.01,0:24:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, say...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:09.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this letter threatening a murder!?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of the clocks is slow by 0.5 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.30,0:24:29.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THE GUARDIANS OF TIME'S SWORD\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.53,0:24:48.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.38,0:24:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six o'Clock
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.14,0:24:52.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of 6:00 PM, it's the time when Detective Conan starts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.91,0:24:53.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excluding some locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.88,0:24:54.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay tuned!
